{"tid":1087920,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"ICONIC H的熱狗細咗好多。。。","createTime":"2019-04-01T16:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T10:10:57.000Z","uid":71237,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f378d3862b5d0a3a368009cdfa98f531d9a9ab1d","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:06:43.000Z","msg":"以前鍾意去食ICONIC H的黑松露森林熱狗。<br />\n大大塊黑松露蛋加上多到爆嘅熱融芝士真係幾好食，以前隔兩三個星期就會食一次。<br />\n<br />\n最近一年無去，再去嘅時候發現縮咗水勁多。<br />\n佢裝熱狗個盒size無變到，但係熱狗明顯縮水咗好多，真係令人好失望。<br />\n如果我無記錯，佢由2016年到而家無加價。（雖然本身已經偏貴）<br />\n但我真係情願佢加價，都唔想熱狗大幅縮水。身為熟客真係好失望。<br />\n<br />\n2015年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PPyy9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PPyy9a.jpg&h=c3d50682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2mJbZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2mJbZd.png&h=2471604e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得依間嘢好多策略都錯咗。<br />\n有一段時間佢瘋狂出啲貴價食材，例如鴨肝熱狗、鰻魚熱狗、安格斯熱狗。<br />\n但係依啲嘢配埋熱狗根本太heavy又唔夾，依啲gimmick嘢淨係吸到人地試一次就算，但係留唔到變熟客。如果我想食鰻魚，點解我唔去日式專門店食？<br />\n<br />\n依間嘢又試過喺港島區開分店。果陣會派優惠卷，仲有lunch set。<br />\n但係有一次試過叫佢啲五十幾蚊嘅lunch set，點知熱狗入面條腸竟然係廚師腸。<br />\n我都明白做生意艱難，但係太大貪cut成本只會死得更快。<br />\n有冇其他巴絲有同感？"},{"pid":"f32dfd8b16dd8f87f82319aa53822ef4929c335c","tid":1087920,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"縮到條腸突出黎啦"},{"pid":"075f2f09de1b947f847e46d933373c798993a9bf","tid":1087920,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"太貴啦 仲要一個set食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同區大把平靚正"},{"pid":"2d0578dfa7c4ff63b5f3be3cfc0b322727defc29","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"去openrice睇圖，真係細得可憐<br />\n好心佢熱狗縮水就用返一個細啲嘅盒啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto2/photo/X/QSK/05AJ929AA1F29E7CDD1CBCpx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto2%2Fphoto%2FX%2FQSK%2F05AJ929AA1F29E7CDD1CBCpx.jpg&h=0024d6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static6.orstatic.com/userphoto2/photo/V/OV6/04WTO94CEE7D04DAECF130px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic6.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto2%2Fphoto%2FV%2FOV6%2F04WTO94CEE7D04DAECF130px.jpg&h=99cb3889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static8.orstatic.com/userphoto2/photo/U/OFK/04TQSN76D82BD8C6D49ECCpx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic8.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto2%2Fphoto%2FU%2FOFK%2F04TQSN76D82BD8C6D49ECCpx.jpg&h=fddd83f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"291bbd3baeae60085f26e8bd748c774c92f872f3","tid":1087920,"uid":5112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"紅磡果間我睇佢都頂唔到幾耐,搞搞下又做埋飯<br />\n<br />\n又做埋漢堡,越黎越吊命feel<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我之前都好鐘意食4重奏加蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb7cf8ab8e62a630217fbad54cffd9b9a77f9cd","tid":1087920,"uid":86943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:10:40.000Z","msg":"大鰻狗由一條鰻魚縮到冇半條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b45f2e7eb3d1f4eefa1540bb3164677ba24d57","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYKraeP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYKraeP.png&h=4e94c837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個好笑。<br />\n店主喺ig問大家會揀鰻魚飯定係鰻魚熱狗，結果8成人都揀鰻魚飯。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連自己ig嘅followers都唔揀鰻魚熱狗，你就知道根本唔掂啦</span>。<br />\n<br />\n店主當然希望人均消費愈高愈好，但唔係盲目賣貴價食材就可以做到。<br />\nICONIC H的做法同荃灣的肉餅哥好相似。<br />\n肉餅哥賣原隻龍蝦肉餅、黑松露帆立貝肉餅、足三兩花膠肉餅飯、鵝肝肉餅。<br />\n有少少常識一聽就知道唔會好食。<br />\n依種做生意的方法最多呃到唔識食嘅人食一兩次，根本吸引唔到回頭客。"},{"pid":"cbd23a0761ca4ae90da4525c600fe98fbeda522f","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMr5qRR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMr5qRR.png&h=3369b6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xc1875i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXc1875i.png&h=b340a883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海膽熱狗真係亂咁嚟<br />\n感覺店主根本唔知道自己咩產品最好食<br />\n一味推貴價食材呃唔識食嘅傻仔<br />\n<br />\n創新唔係唔得<br />\n但前題係要靠basic款穩住一班熟客先。<br />\n好似m記KFC吉野家都成日出新款, 而依啲新款九成都係伏。<br />\n但點解佢地唔會做臭自己個名? 就係因為佢地有一堆basic款支撐住。<br />\n<br />\n就算吉野家嘅海鮮龍蝦湯飯再難食。<br />\n客人中伏就後都仍然會繼續幫趁吉野家。<br />\n因為佢地知道牛肉飯, 雞飯嘅味道唔會變。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得ICONIC H應該主力sell啲最好食嘅款 (e.g. 黑松露森林)<br />\n海膽, 鰻魚, 鵝肝, 三文魚依啲都可以賣, 但應該用期間限定嘅方式去做。<br />\n例如4月海膽, 5月鰻魚, 6月鵝肝咁。<br />\n咁樣keep到新鮮感之餘, 又可以用最好食嘅basic款去儲熟客。"},{"pid":"7767a271b41afb6fe7c1e0e53852a09c840d1788","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"頭先打漏咗一段<br />\n<br />\n就算吉野家嘅海鮮龍蝦湯飯再難食。<br />\n客人中伏就後都仍然會繼續幫趁吉野家。<br />\n因為佢地知道牛肉飯, 雞飯嘅味道唔會變。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果有個新客第一次就食海膽熱狗。<br />\n佢覺得唔好食之後就永遠唔會再嚟。</span>"},{"pid":"409e1fa6a2aabbc22604c708a122bd6c16ce3b2c","tid":1087920,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T23:36:00.000Z","msg":"3年前食都好難食wo ching"},{"pid":"0fd48657061cd5347e31cd2f3c5c1207f304973f","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"409e1fa6a2aabbc22604c708a122bd6c16ce3b2c","tid":1087920,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T23:36:00.000Z","msg":"3年前食都好難食wo ching"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:15:38.000Z","msg":"你嗰陣食邊款熱狗呀？"},{"pid":"89788855638d2ff575c1728756d94ea4b0369d61","tid":1087920,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fd48657061cd5347e31cd2f3c5c1207f304973f","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"409e1fa6a2aabbc22604c708a122bd6c16ce3b2c","tid":1087920,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T23:36:00.000Z","msg":"3年前食都好難食wo ching"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:15:38.000Z","msg":"你嗰陣食邊款熱狗呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:32:31.000Z","msg":"地獄唔知乜"},{"pid":"d6bac002a0ac03c061bcf5c9b3fe69e5515e2b40","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"291bbd3baeae60085f26e8bd748c774c92f872f3","tid":1087920,"uid":5112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"紅磡果間我睇佢都頂唔到幾耐,搞搞下又做埋飯<br />\n<br />\n又做埋漢堡,越黎越吊命feel<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我之前都好鐘意食4重奏加蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T01:44:01.000Z","msg":"佢啲芝士真係正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdf5e75131cbaedca23ebff06c09febf9789b3c","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e9b8ba09f20427869e772292b013a4f135f56c","tid":1087920,"uid":146024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪香港人似乎唔太鐘意食熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食過幾間得呢間算做得長"},{"pid":"79c4b9a1712c04b0cff59408476e844751b82a75","tid":1087920,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e9b8ba09f20427869e772292b013a4f135f56c","tid":1087920,"uid":146024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪香港人似乎唔太鐘意食熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食過幾間得呢間算做得長"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:29: